## Run Locally

Clone the project

```bash
  git clone https://github.com/KocakAli/libgen-cli.git
```

Go to the project directory

```bash
  cd libgen-cli
```

Install dependencies

```bash
  pip install .
```

Start the cli

```bash
  libgen-cli --help
```

